The rollout gateway (src/agentcore_rl_toolkit/rollout_gateway/) adapts code from
slime, notably:
  - trajectory.py  — TrajectoryManager, TurnRecord, MessageNode, and the
                     CLEAN/REALIGN/FORK drift classification, adapted from
                     slime/agent/trajectory.py (made torch-free).
  - adapters/      — OpenAIAdapter, AnthropicAdapter, and the shared BaseAdapter
                     pipeline, adapted from slime/agent/adapters/.
  - parsing.py     — output-parsing helpers, adapted from slime/agent/parsing.py.
